title: Cornish Pasty with Jon Gabrus (LIVE)
itunes:title: Cornish Pasty with Jon Gabrus (LIVE)
description:
Jon Gabrus (Action Boyz, High and Mighty) joins the 'boys to discuss their fiber intake before a review of Cornish Pasty. Plus, another edition of The Wiger Challenge. Recorded live at Stand Up Live in Phoenix 4/28/22.

Sources for this week's intro:

https://www.npr.org/2021/03/11/975663437/march-11-2020-the-day-everything-changed
